::Killfest/Incarcinator/Scyther::

Killfest growls under his breath as he recieves Darkmouse's 
transmission, turning to Motormaster. "Something's come up back at 
base. One of my soldiers will be here to pick me up soon."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Incarcinator, recieving a series of orders from Killfest, lifts off of 
Mangolian ground, flying toward the Stunticon base.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Scyther also recieves some orders, turning to Pinsir. "Lets get back 
to base. There's nothing to do here."
